020package org.tquadrat.foundation.javacomposer;
021
022import static org.apiguardian.api.API.Status.STABLE;
023
024import java.lang.reflect.ParameterizedType;
025import java.lang.reflect.Type;
026import java.util.LinkedHashMap;
027import java.util.List;
028
029import org.apiguardian.api.API;
030import org.tquadrat.foundation.annotation.ClassVersion;
031import org.tquadrat.foundation.javacomposer.internal.ParameterizedTypeNameImpl;
032
033/**
034 *  The specialisation of
035 *  {@link TypeName}
036 *  for parameterised types.
037 *
038 *  @author Square,Inc.
039 *  @modified Thomas Thrien - thomas.thrien@tquadrat.org
040 *  @version $Id: ParameterizedTypeName.java 1085 2024-01-05 16:23:28Z tquadrat $
041 *  @since 0.0.5
042 *
043 *  @UMLGraph.link
044 */
045@ClassVersion( sourceVersion = "$Id: ParameterizedTypeName.java 1085 2024-01-05 16:23:28Z tquadrat $" )
046@API( status = STABLE, since = "0.0.5" )
047public sealed interface ParameterizedTypeName extends TypeName
048    permits ParameterizedTypeNameImpl
049{
050        /*---------*\
051    ====** Methods **==========================================================
052        \*---------*/
053    /**
054     *  {@inheritDoc}
055     */
056    @Override
057    public ParameterizedTypeName annotated( final List<AnnotationSpec> annotations );
058
059    /**
060     *  Returns a parameterised type, applying the given type arguments to the
061     *  given raw type.
062     *
063     *  @param  rawType The class name for the new type.
064     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
065     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
066     */
067    @SuppressWarnings( "ClassReferencesSubclass" )
068    @API( status = STABLE, since = "0.2.0" )
069    public static ParameterizedTypeName from( final Class<?> rawType, final Type... typeArguments )
070    {
071        final var retValue = ParameterizedTypeNameImpl.from( rawType, typeArguments );
072
073        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
074        return retValue;
075    }   //  from()
076
077    /**
078     *  Returns a parameterised type, applying the given type arguments to the
079     *  given raw type.
080     *
081     *  @param  rawType The class name for the new type.
082     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
083     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
084     */
085    @SuppressWarnings( "ClassReferencesSubclass" )
086    @API( status = STABLE, since = "0.2.0" )
087    public static ParameterizedTypeName from( final ClassName rawType, final TypeName... typeArguments )
088    {
089        final var retValue = ParameterizedTypeNameImpl.from( rawType, typeArguments );
090
091        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
092        return retValue;
093    }   //  from()
094
095    /**
096     *  Returns a parameterised type equivalent to the given type.
097     *
098     *  @param  type    The other type.
099     *  @return The new instance of {@code ParameterizedTypeName}.
100     */
101    @SuppressWarnings( "ClassReferencesSubclass" )
102    @API( status = STABLE, since = "0.2.0" )
103    public static ParameterizedTypeName from( final ParameterizedType type )
104    {
105        final var retValue = ParameterizedTypeNameImpl.from( type, new LinkedHashMap<>() );
106
107        //---* Done *----------------------------------------------------------
108        return retValue;
109    }   //  from()
110
111    /**
112     *  Returns a new {@code ParameterizedTypeName} instance for the specified
113     *  name as nested inside this class.
114     *
115     *  @param  name    The name for the nested class.
116     *  @return The new nested class.
117     */
118    public ParameterizedTypeName nestedClass( final CharSequence name );
119
120    /**
121     *  Returns a new {@code ParameterizedTypeName} instance for the specified
122     *  name as nested inside this class, with the specified type arguments.
123     *
124     *  @param  name    The name for the nested class.
125     *  @param  typeArguments   The type arguments.
126     *  @return The new nested class.
127     */
128    public ParameterizedTypeName nestedClass( final CharSequence name, final List<TypeName> typeArguments );
129
130    /**
131     *  Returns the raw type for this parameterised type name.
132     *
133     *  @return The raw type.
134     */
135    public ClassName rawType();
136
137    /**
138     *  Returns the type arguments for this parameterised type name.
139     *
140     *  @return The type arguments.
141     */
142    public List<TypeName> typeArguments();
143
144    /**
145     *  {@inheritDoc}
146     */
147    @Override
148    public TypeName withoutAnnotations();
149}
150//  interface ParameterizedTypeName
151
